description: Along with everything else that makes Las Vegas such a lucky place, is I LUV COTTON CANDY: the truck that serves up the delicious sugary fluff that makes the world a more dandy place. You’ll also find delightfully sweet cupcakes and hot crunchy popcorn, and all these treats are sure to just hit the spot. Come out and try this truck’s creations, and you too will just LUV this street sensation.
name: I LUV COTTON CANDY
